# Progress

`TuffProgress` is the lightweight compatibility entry for standard linear progress rows. It forwards a small prop set to `TxProgressBar` with outside text, plain mask styling, and `strokeWidth` mapped to bar height.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/progress/src/TxProgress.vue`, `progress.test.ts`, and `index.ts`.

